additionalProperty.name: Ingredients
additionalProperty.value: Sugar, wheat flour, white chocolate chips (9%) (sugar, milk solids, cocoa butter, emulsifier (soy lecithin), natural vanilla flavour), dark chocolate chips (6%) (sugar, cocoa mass, cocoa butter, natural vanilla flavour, emulsifier (soy lecithin)), cocoa (3.5%), vegetable oil, salt, maize starch, raising agents (sodium bicarbonate, sodium aluminium phosphate). White chocolate contains 21% cocoa solids. Dark chocolate contains 41% cocoa solids.

additionalProperty.name: Allergen
additionalProperty.value: May Be Present Egg, Contains Milk, Contains Wheat

description: A decadent moist and chewy chocolate brownie, full of milk and white chocolate chips. A perfect treat for dessert or a little afternoon snack.
name: Triple Chocolate Fudge Brownie Mix
